		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just use NROM.  It's the easiest to program for &amp; you can get them just about anywhere.  Pull any SMB or Duck Hunt (wouldn't go w/ SMB/Duck Hunt though, higher chance of blobbed ROM's) cart &amp; desolder the ROMs.

		

